
cocaine, a sniffer written in C

FEATURES (very basic)
- sniff IP, TCP, UDP, ICMP, ARP
- tcpdump filters
- IPv4 checksum verification
- DNS names resolution (to test)
- Display payload of TCP packets

TODO
- output in HTLM format. Useful for example when we want to check the sniffer results via web

COMPILE

gcc -lm -lpcap -Wall -g sniff.c -o ../bin/cocaine
